    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You learn how to amplify your rune-powered transformation. As a result, your size can increase to Huge when you use Giant's Might, and while you are that size, your Reach and Speed are both increased by 5 feet.</p><p>Additionally, your weapons and Unarmed Strikes are considered oversized depending on your size and apply to you.  Double the weapon dice if the you are Large, triple the weapon dice you are Huge, and quadruple the weapon dice you are Gargantuan. For example, a Huge Rune Knight an appropriately sized greataxe deals 3d12 slashing damage (plus their Strength bonus), instead of the normal 1d12.</p>",
